text: Iquiracetima aspasia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1995. It is known from Ecuador and Peru.BioLib.cz - Iquiracetima aspasia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1995
